OL,3,CMan accused of dumping 27 tonnes of
OL,4,Cwaste in country lane appears in court
OL,6,FA man who allegedly dumped 27 tonnes
OL,7,Fof waste which blocked off access to
OL,8,Fhomes and businesses on a country lane
OL,9,Fhas appeared in court.
OL,11,FDarren Sheen, 39, offered no
OL,12,Findication of plea to a raft of
OL,13,Fcharges faced by him and a business,
OL,14,FFusion Engineering Ltd, at Cannock
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,17,FThe charges relate to a huge mound of
OL,18,Ffly-tipped waste that appeared on the
OL,19,Fnight of January 19 in Watery Lane on
OL,20,Fthe outskirts of Lichfield in
OL,21,FStaffordshire.
