OL,6,FSheen, who wore a blue shirt and tie
OL,7,Ffor the 10-minute hearing, of Grange
OL,8,FRoad in Uttoxeter, is accused of
OL,9,Fcausing danger to road users,
OL,10,Fsubmitting controlled waste likely to
OL,11,Fcause pollution or harm to human
OL,12,Fhealth, driving a motor vehicle
OL,13,Fdangerously, failing without
OL,14,Freasonable excuse to record data on a
OL,15,Fdriver's card, wilful obstruction of a
OL,16,Fhighway, failure to take measures when
OL,17,Fmanaging extractive waste to prevent
OL,18,Fcontraventions and the escape of
OL,19,Fwaste, handling, controlling or
OL,20,Ftransferring controlled waste without
OL,21,Ftaking reasonable measures and
OL,22,Fdepositing rubbish within 15 feet of
OL,23,Fthe centre of a highway.
