OL,6,FLichfield District Council began an
OL,7,Finvestigation after the waste, which
OL,8,Fmeasured over 20 metres long and two
OL,9,Fmetres high, was dumped and
OL,10,Fcontractors used a mechanical digger
OL,11,Fto clear the road and restore access
OL,12,Fto the two-lane route the next morning.
