OL,3,CMan accused of dumping 27 tonnes of
OL,4,Cwaste in country lane appears in court
OL,6,FProsecutor Mark Jackson told the court
OL,7,Fit was their case that Sheen got into
OL,8,Fa Volvo HGV which had a trailer of
OL,9,Funtreated waste attached at the
OL,10,Fcompany's unit in Pasturefields
OL,11,FEnterprise Park in Great Haywood and
OL,12,Fdrove 23km to Watery Lane where he
OL,13,Fallegedly reversed the vehicle and
OL,14,Fdumped the waste.
OL,16,FHe said Sheen accepted in interview
OL,17,Fthat he had driven the vehicle and had
OL,18,Fgone to the area, but that he had gone
OL,19,Fout that night to "test the brakes" of
OL,20,Fthe HGV.
